            Our goal is to make our patients feel like they are family. As a practice, we focus on preventative medicine, health screenings, and helping our community find solutions to the health challenges they face.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
            Our board certified physicians will work with you to achieve the best possible state of health and well being. We believe in building lasting relationships with our patients based on trust, communication, and comprehensive care.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mt-8">
          <div class="bg-primary-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
